AddressInfo.Title: Yadkin Valley Experience
AddressInfo.AccessComments: This EV charging station is located in downtown Elkin at the new heritage and trails center, one block south of Main Street in historic downtown Elkin.  This is one of two locations in the downtown (the other is two blocks north at Town Hall). The charging station is located towards the back of the center, on the right (or east) side of the building.  There is room for ADA vehicle accessibility and no fees for charging services. There are also restrooms on site.

GeneralComments: Telefonix  L2,  Low current Level 2 PowerPost EVSE
